data.description: Step into practicality with this expansive two-story residence in the coveted Enclave at Ventana Community. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home spans 1925 Sq Ft and offers a modern open floorplan. The tiled first floor seamlessly integrates a chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, a spacious living room, and a dining room—ideal for entertaining guests. Ascend to the carpeted second floor, where a versatile loft awaits, perfect for use as a media room. All four bedrooms, including a palatial owner's suite with a lavish private bathroom and a generously sized walk-in closet, can be found on this level. Conveniently located on the second floor, the laundry room makes chores a breeze. Step outside and revel in the EXTRA-LARGE backyard, providing an ideal space for outdoor entertainment. The Ventana Community itself offers amenities such as a sparkling pool, park, and pickle ball court. With the added convenience of easy access to HWY I-75, reaching Downtown Tampa, Channelside, Ybor City, and the beach becomes a seamless endeavor. Elevate your living experience in this stunning home within a thriving community.
